After assisting in helping Voyager return to the Alpha Quadrant, Starfleet splits the Hazard Team up among different assignments. Two years later in 2380, Captain Jean-Luc Picard of the Enterprise-E is the first to see the use for a Hazard Team, and transfers Munro and many of the old members of the team to the Enterprise...
